They just know that their mug doesn't say #1 Dad anymore and that has hurt their confidence.

The next morning something interesting happens. All of the #1 Mom mugs have also changed to show their actual ranking. The moms are also offended and their confidence seems to be shook too. Again, neither parent even knows what these rankings actually mean. They just know that their mug no longer says #1 Mom or Dad on it.

A news brief covers the story and goes on about the effects that this change in mugs has had on families. Stress levels and anxiety were increased. The video also reported that social media is flooded with posts from parents, upset that a mug they bought has changed.
